channel.title: Gnome Agility Course. Rep +
channel.description:
Does anyone out there know how to add the 2nd and third floor of the gnome agility course?
What i mean is when i click the climb-over obstacle net (the 2nd obstacle of the agility course) it goes up a floor but there is nothing up there. Does anyone know how to add that floor and the floor above of the agility course?
Btw im using Black pearl's source. If you need more info please say so.
Rep + for whoever fixes it.
By the way when i use the obstacle and see nothing. For some reason when i relog it shows it
